                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2106" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0107</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8911 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">同瑞集团ERP实施的缘起缘落：一波三折，终成泡影</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Ups and Downs in the Failing Implementation of ERP System of Tongrui Enterprise</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">尹裴，王洪伟等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">同济大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">同瑞集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业资源计划；业务流程重组；企业管理变革；信息化建设；信息系统开发</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning); Business Process Reengineering; Management Reform; Information Construction; Development of Information Systems</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着市场经济的深入发展，全球经济一体化的转变，中国企业的外部竞争压力越来越大。同时，变化莫测的市场要求企业管理做到随机应变，并且根据客户的需求不断调整。因此，为了提高竞争力，适应市场的快速变化，企业急需信息化建设，实施ERP(Enterprise Resource Planning，企业资源计划)系统。本案例描述了同瑞集团进行ERP建设的全过程，包括企业信息化战略决策、ERP选型、ERP系统规划、分析、设计和实施等。通过对ERP建设过程中遇到的问题进行叙述和讨论，表现了ERP系统对企业长期发展的重要性，以及ERP建设的不易。虽然同瑞集团的ERP实施最后以失败告终，但是对于企业ERP建设应该注意的问题进行分析与总结，例如企业管理变革的重要性、信息系统的社会—技术特征、ERP与业务流程重组的互补性以及系统开发的“一把手”原则等，也是值得思考和重视的。此外，本案例还为企业进行ERP供应商选择提供了一定的参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the further development of market economy and the transformation of global economy integration, there is increasing external competition pressure for Chinese company. In the meantime, the unpredictable market demand requires companies to adapt themselves to changing circumstances and continually make adjustment to customers’ needs. Therefore, in order to enhance competiveness and adapt to the rapid change of market, companies are badly in need of information construction, and one powerful means of informatization is the implementation of ERP system (Enterprise Resource Planning). This case describes the whole process of the implementation of ERP system in Tongrui enterprise, including the decision making of informatization strategy, the selection of ERP system provider, the planning, analyzing, designing and implementing of ERP system. Through narration and discussion of the problems encountered in the process of implementing ERP system, the importance of ERP system to company’s long-run development and the difficulty of ERP implementation are indicated in this case. Although the implementation of ERP system in Tongrui enterprise is ended in a failure, it’s worth a while to think and summarize the problems in the implementation of ERP system for companies, such as the importance of management innovation, the social-technical features of information systems, the complementary relationship between ERP and BPR, and the leadership principle in the development of information systems. Furthermore, this case also provides a certain reference value for companies to select ERP system providers.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理信息系统》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业信息化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-09</td>
                            </tr>
